Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:16.79,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}If I spend more time alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.79,0:22:21.21,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I thought I would get used to it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:27.33,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I'm a coward with a a straight face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.33,0:22:32.15,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,223)\be2}But in reality I was afraid inside
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.15,0:22:36.97,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}It shouldn't have been like this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:42.38,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}Only excuses keep piling up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.66,0:22:48.71,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}I will be forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.71,0:22:52.76,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}From your memory someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.99,0:23:01.44,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}For a few more decades let's go for a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:05.97,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}To collect the things that have been dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:11.09,ED - E,,0,0,0,,{\fad(123,123)\be2}No matter what my future is
